Date of start of the outbreak: 13 Mar 2013
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Affected animals:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Equidae / 9 / 1 / 0 / 0 / 0
Affected population: 5-year-old Anglo-Arabian horse used for sport.

